{"type":null,"faqId":33898,"title":"如何快速整理桌面上的图标？","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.p1{margin-left:0.39375in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.p2{margin-left:0.39375in;margin-top:0.108333334in;margin-bottom:0.108333334in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span>开启动作和手势开关后，点击“摇一摇”并勾选“自动对齐桌面图标”复选框。在主屏幕编辑状态下，摇晃手机即可将桌面图标自动对齐。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=108604\" style=\"width:2.2916667in;height:3.988889in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=108605\" style=\"width:2.2590277in;height:3.9666667in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":144,"faqType":"其他","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"8600","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Others","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1436748760000,"seriesProductName":"PLK-AL10,PLK-CL00,PLK-TL00,PLK-TL01H,PLK-UL00","visitedTimes":47,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"整理,桌面图标","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}